TgjGpVjOMnDQ&oe=66DAF750"}, "display_name": "Dark Days", "keywords": ["Thriller", "Horror", "Adventure", "Escaperoom", "Storydriven"], "long_description": "The team that created White Night has gathered once again to offer you a hauntingly unique VR experience.\n\nSomewhere between Twin Peaks and The X-\u00adFiles, Dark Days is a new fantastic virtual reality adventure. You will have to discover what\u2019s going on with an eerie desert motel and its surroundings by solving a number of puzzles. Immerse yourself in the rich environments you will come across, but be careful and smart! Something is roaming around you, a terrifying presence that you need to keep away from by all means.\n\n\u274f A supernatural adventure full of revelations that tells the story of Jade Lacroix, a lost young writer who has to investigate weird events in order to survive, while fighting her inner fears.\n\n\u274f Accessible gameplay and random puzzles inspired by escape rooms games\n\n\u274f A terrifying presence will haunt your progression\u2026 be prepared for jump scares!", "short_description": "Somewhere between Twin Peaks and The X-\u00adFiles, Dark Days is a new fantastic virtual reality adventure. You will have to discover what\u2019s going on with an eerie desert motel and its surroundings by solving a number of puzzles. Immerse yourself in the rich environments you will come across, but be careful and smart! Something is roaming around you, a terrifying presence that you need to keep away from by all means."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": null, "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Oculus Studio", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://www.parallel-studio.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": null, "genres": ["HORROR", "NARRATIVE", "ADVENTURE", "EXPLORATION", "PUZZLE"], "has_in_app_ads": fal